All of the scripts contained in this directory are based on sed & awk, 2nd Edition from O'Reilly Media, written by Dale Dougherty & Arnold Robbins.  

The scripts that appear in this directory are derivatives that I've created based on my readings.  

The scripts that appear in sedawk2progs subdirectory were created by the books authors.

These scripts are publically available at https://resources.oreilly.com/examples/9781565922259.
